---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — Campbell K9s"
  description="Terms and conditions for Campbell K9s training, boarding, and adventure hike services."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-28 sm:px-10 sm:py-36 lg:px-8 lg:py-44">
    <p class="caption text-brand-accent">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="mt-6 font-serif text-4xl leading-tight sm:text-5xl">
      Terms of Service
    </h1>
    <p class="caption mt-4 text-brand-primary/50">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-12 hairline max-w-[3rem]"></div>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-10 text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-primary/80 sm:text-lg">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-brand-primary">Services</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Campbell K9s provides dog training, board and train programs,
          off-leash adventure hikes, and premium overnight boarding services in
          the Greater Boston and Providence, Rhode Island areas. All services are
          provided by appointment and are subject to availability.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-brand-primary">Client Responsibilities</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Clients are responsible for disclosing all relevant health, behavioral,
          and vaccination history for their dog prior to the start of any program.
          Dogs must be current on core vaccinations. Campbell K9s reserves the
          right to decline service for any dog deemed unsuitable for the program.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-brand-primary">Liability</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Campbell K9s takes every precaution to ensure the safety of dogs in
          our care. However, we cannot guarantee against accidents or injuries
          inherent to outdoor activities and group settings. Clients accept these
          risks when enrolling in our programs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-brand-primary">Cancellation</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Cancellation and refund terms are established at the time of enrollment
          and set out in your service agreement. Please contact us directly with
          any questions regarding your specific arrangement.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-brand-primary">Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Questions about these terms can be directed to{" "}
          <a
            href="mailto:k9campbellmatt@gmail.com"
            class="border-b border-brand-primary/30 pb-0.5 transition-colors hover:border-brand-accent hover:text-brand-accent"
          >
            k9campbellmatt@gmail.com
          </a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
